project_descr: While women make up over half of the population and provide significant contribution to society, a disparity remains in terms of the fulfillment of their needs and the services and protections afforded to them by the government.

outputs.output_descr: Research and dialogue will be conducted to help establish and inform a wider programme that seeks to promote women's rights in the Philippines through: 1) strengthening gender justice, and 2) Mainstreaming gender concerns in national and local plans

document_name: 107467 Strengthening Women's Rights in the Philippines
project_title: strengthening women’s rights in the philippines
